review: yes, cheesecake factory is pretty obnoxious, but it's one of my guilty pleasures! my faves: fried macaroni and cheese balls!!!! popcorn shrimp orange chicken four cheese pasta chicken farfalle luisiana chicken pasta sun-dried tomato fettucini vanilla bean, kahlua, oreo, tuxedo & cookie dough cheesecakes ....and the pumpernickel bread!
the service here stunk.  the waiter screwed up the simple things I asked him to do.  the food was ok, the atmosphere was ok...... I would go back only if I got a different waiter.
